# Orchestrator Environment

This project uses `.orchestrator/` as the canonical multi-agent configuration source.

When working in this repository:

- Read policies from `.orchestrator/config/policies.json`
- Use skills listed in `.orchestrator/skills/registry.json`
- Persist durable knowledge under `.orchestrator/memory/`
- Write runtime artifacts under `.orchestrator/runtime/`

Do not create parallel agent configuration trees. Extend `.orchestrator/` instead.

See `docs/agent-environment.md` for the full layout.
